trans-unit.source: Represents a query that tests whether the action of a message is one of a specified set of actions.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en spørring som tester om handlingen for en melding inngår i et angitt sett med handlinger.

trans-unit.source: It is invalid to construct an ActionMessageFilter with no actions.
trans-unit.target: Det er ugyldig for å lage en ActionMessageFilter med ingen handlinger.

trans-unit.source: This type is serializable as a <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractAttribute>.
trans-unit.target: Denne typen er serializable som <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractAttribute>.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractAttribute>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of this class with the set of actions for which it tests.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av denne klassen med et sett med handlinger som testes.

trans-unit.source: If the array of `actions` provided to populate the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter> contains duplicate actions, the duplicates are removed and only one of them is added to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en rekke `actions` angitt til å fylle ut den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter>inneholder dupliserte handlinger duplikater er fjernet, og bare én av dem er lagt til <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601> of `actions` contained in the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter> is accessed by the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter.Actions%2A> property and cannot be modified after the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter> object is instantiated.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>av `actions` i den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter>brukes av den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter.Actions%2A>egenskapen og kan ikke endres etter den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter>objektet startes.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter.Actions%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ActionMessageFilter> </xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>
